window.bookSummaryJSON = "<p>When a massive meteor lights up the sky over the remote island of Kerguelen, the world holds its breath. In Birchwood, Colorado, Dan McCarthy gets to work.&nbsp;&nbsp;</p> <p>Following his incredible experiences of the previous year, Dan knows this was no natural occurrence. The Messengers are back - to finish what they started - and they didn't come all this way for nothing....&nbsp;</p> <p><i>Not Alone: Second Contact</i> is the long-awaited sequel to <i>Not Alone</i>, an Audible \"Best of 2016\" finalist.</p>";